BOUNDSPEC SEGMENT IJ 71 70 80 70 VARIABLE FILE 0 'Projects/Porto_ilha_202404/swan_domains/boundary_202404/specs_n_7.spc2d 

BOUNDSPEC SEGMENT IJ 81 70 90 70 VARIABLE FILE 0 'Projects/Porto_ilha_202404/swan_domains/boundary_202404/specs_n_8.spc2d 

